data.text:
List of Singles for Tom Petty and the Heartbreakers

The list of top singles for Tom Petty and the Heartbreakers come from the Playback.fm charts. Chart appearances and counts span from 1900-2016 only. Chart appearances include Pop, R&B, Country and Rock. Other genres are not yet included. This list only includes the first billed artist for the given track. It may include writing credits and featured credits in the near future. The data is for entertainment purposes only.
